snippet.title: Pac-Man World (PS1) Gameplay
snippet.description: This is Gameplay for Pac-Man World on the Sony Playstation. This game was released for the 20th Anniversary of the original Pac-Man, and is not only a really fun 3D platformer, but also has a maze mode, and the arcade original added. Really fun game, give it a look if you have never given it a play.
